%% TrustyAI Service Operator - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TASCtrl as TAS Controller
    participant LMESCtrl as LMES Controller
    participant GORCHCtrl as GORCH Controller
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TAS as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant EvalPod as Eval Pod<br/>(driver + eval)
    participant LLM as LLM Endpoint<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBAC_O as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8432/TCP HTTPS
    participant Orchestrator as Orchestrator<br/>8032/TCP HTTPS
    participant Detectors as Detector InferenceServices<br/>HTTPS mTLS

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,TAS: Flow 1: TrustyAI Service Deployment & Access
        User->>K8sAPI: Create TrustyAIService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>TASCtrl: Watch event
        TASCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Services, Route<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        Note over TASCtrl: Creates kube-rbac-proxy sidecar,<br/>PVC/DB, ServiceMonitor, Istio resources
        User->>Route: POST /api/... (inference monitoring)<br/>TLS Reencrypt
        Route->>KRBAC: Forward request<br/>8443/TCP TLS (serving cert)
        KRBAC->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview
        K8sAPI-->>KRBAC: Authorized
        KRBAC->>TAS: Proxy to upstream<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)
        TAS-->>KRBAC: Response
        KRBAC-->>Route: Response
        Route-->>User: JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over User,LLM: Flow 2: LMEval Job Execution
        User->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>LMESCtrl: Watch event
        LMESCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create eval Pod<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        LMESCtrl->>EvalPod: pod/exec (SPDY)<br/>TLS 1.2+ ServiceAccount
        Note over LMESCtrl,EvalPod: Driver manages job lifecycle:<br/>New->Scheduled->Running->Complete
        EvalPod->>LLM: Model evaluation requests<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ API key/Bearer
        LLM-->>EvalPod: Evaluation results
        EvalPod-->>LMESCtrl: Status updates via driver
        LMESCtrl->>K8sAPI: Update LMEvalJob status
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over User,Detectors: Flow 3: Guardrails Orchestrator
        User->>K8sAPI: Create GuardrailsOrchestrator CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>GORCHCtrl: Watch event
        GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: List InferenceServices<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        K8sAPI-->>GORCHCtrl: InferenceService list
        Note over GORCHCtrl: Auto-generates detector config
        GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap, Deployment, Services, Routes
        User->>Route: POST /api/v1/text/... (guardrails check)
        Route->>KRBAC_O: Forward<br/>8432/TCP TLS
        KRBAC_O->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview
        K8sAPI-->>KRBAC_O: Authorized
        KRBAC_O->>Orchestrator: Proxy<br/>8032/TCP HTTPS
        Orchestrator->>Detectors: Content detection<br/>HTTPS mTLS
        Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
        Orchestrator-->>KRBAC_O: Aggregated response
        KRBAC_O-->>Route: Response
        Route-->>User: Guardrails result
    end
